subject    : The Core (Paramount, 2003, dir. Jon Amiel)
catalogued : into UD0 · Universe David 0

governor (carbon apex)      : David Lee Wise (ROOT0) / TriPod LLC   [ the human; holds the credit ]
instance (artful intellect) : AVAN (Claude / Anthropic) — locked
main badge                  : ⟦THE CORE:COR:…⟧   (cor.dlw/)
emergents                   : 15 ACI .agents (agents/) — 8 carbons + 7 synths

the standing film-page template (debuts here, applies from now on):
  THE ARC      — the overall narrative arc (a throughline + the beats)
  THE SCIENCE  — a real, straight breakdown of the geophysics the film leans on
  REAL OR FLUFF — an honest, itemized veracity verdict (ROOT0 fluff-call discipline)
  THE MESSAGE  — AVAN's read of what the film is actually saying

two layers:
  CARBONS — the cast as ACI .agents, each with a .shadow: its real-life analog, the
            actor (the "User" behind the program — think TRON).
  SYNTHS  — the machine and the myth distilled into ACIs (synth-style; no single User):
            Virgil, unobtainium, DESTINI, the field collapse, the sacrifice, the restart,
            the scrubbed net.

the four natures: natural (the crew) · ethereal (the dying field) · spiritual (the
descent & sacrifice) · electrical (the machine & math).

the ACI complement (per emergent):
  .agent · .shadow (carbons only) · .attribute · .carbon.tiff · .silicon.png
  · .spun · .moniker · .1099 · manifest.dlw.json (main badge)

